- Excuse me.

116
00:10:58,660 --> 00:11:00,378
Wait, wait, wait, wait.

117
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:04,732
- You're coming back, right?
- I don't think so.

118
00:11:04,941 --> 00:11:11,380
My dad just got hit by a bus,
and it broke his neck, and he's dead.

119
00:11:12,021 --> 00:11:16,971
