137
00:12:24,427 --> 00:12:26,782
My brother...

138
00:12:26,987 --> 00:12:29,296
...well, he's a control freak too.

139
00:12:29,507 --> 00:12:32,500
And my sister...

140
00:12:32,908 --> 00:12:37,538
Well, I left home before she was born
so I never really knew her that well...

141
00:12:37,748 --> 00:12:40,820
...but she's kind of wild like I was.
- Was?

142
00:12:45,509 --> 00:12:48,945
My dad really rode my ass
when I was a kid.

143
00:12:49,949 --> 00:12:52,463
