at a Flock of Seagulls concert...

145
00:12:56,590 --> 00:12:58,865
...and I'm not allowed to go
to concerts for a year.

146
00:12:59,070 --> 00:13:00,628
Your dad worked in a cemetery?

147
00:13:00,830 --> 00:13:04,789
How could a man who's so scared of
everything, who never had an accident...

148
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:09,303
...or a speeding ticket in his entire life,
how could he have a car wreck?

149
00:13:09,511 --> 00:13:14,983
Are you mad at him,
or the fact that we're all gonna die?

150
00:13:15,391 --> 00:13:20,910
- Are you a shrink?
