just fucked a perfect stranger?

155
00:13:35,753 --> 00:13:39,541
And that we both lied
when we said we never did that.

156
00:13:48,514 --> 00:13:52,223
- Wonderful service.
- Yes, it was. Very nice.

157
00:14:02,755 --> 00:14:04,666
She looked so peaceful.
Thank you so much.

158
00:14:04,875 --> 00:14:07,787
- You're welcome.
- Wonderful job.

159
00:14:12,996 --> 00:14:14,634
Did you know that
before you were born...

160
00:14:14,836 --> 00:14:17,794
