that could transport people lying down.

163
00:14:26,957 --> 00:14:29,790
Your father used to joke about that.

164
00:14:29,997 --> 00:14:33,148
"Just drive him around the block
a few more times.

165
00:14:33,357 --> 00:14:36,907
We won't need to stop
at the hospital. "

166
00:14:37,438 --> 00:14:40,396
