207
00:17:23,131 --> 00:17:24,723
But I think I'm having a meltdown...

208
00:17:24,931 --> 00:17:28,719
...and I can't tell if it's Dad being dead
or the crystal, but...

209
00:17:29,091 --> 00:17:31,652
