211
00:17:34,532 --> 00:17:36,682
Don't be a narc.
We smoked pot at Thanksgiving.

212
00:17:36,892 --> 00:17:40,248
Look, I have to go identify
our dead father's body.

213
00:17:40,452 --> 00:17:44,890
