217
00:18:20,896 --> 00:18:24,366
This is what you've been running away
from your whole life, buddy-boy.

218
00:18:24,576 --> 00:18:27,488
Scared the crap out of you
when you were growing up, didn't it?

219
00:18:28,656 --> 00:18:32,855
